sentences: Alexi Murdoch (born 27 December 1973) is a British folk musician and songwriter.
Since his debut in 2002, Murdoch has released two LPs and one EP.
Murdoch moved to the United States in 1992 to study at Duke University, before moving to Los Angeles, California to live with his then-girlfriend.
He self-released the EP Four Songs through independent record stores and website CD Baby in November 2002.
